                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Both Grakata and Prisma Grakata will have a fire rate of 40 / 44.44 / 50 / 57.14 / 66.67 / 80 , despite the Prisma variant having a higher fire rate on its normal firing mode."
