                  "pageId": 1396630,
                  "revisionId": 2729961,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Abilities and mods that modify fire rate have no effect on this alternate fire mode. As a result, mods like Vile Precision and Critical Delay only provide their benefit."
